{"tid":2368270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真心好奇] 究竟中國疫情現時如何?","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T07:41:17.000Z","uid":258345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61648f8f00ffa311024e9f713650ce5c0f4a3b23","tid":2368270,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"打開外媒 近排講中國.國際貿易多左. 然後就一堆文話係因為中國控制到疫情.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如<br />\n<a href=\"https://financialpost.com/executive/executive-summary/posthaste-is-china-eating-the-rest-of-the-worlds-lunch-its-starting-to-look-like-it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinancialpost.com%2Fexecutive%2Fexecutive-summary%2Fposthaste-is-china-eating-the-rest-of-the-worlds-lunch-its-starting-to-look-like-it&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=adaee49d\" target=\"_blank\">https://financialpost.com/executive/executive-summary/posthaste-is-china-eating-the-rest-of-the-worlds-lunch-its-starting-to-look-like-it</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Shahid says China&rsquo;s success containing the virus and its recovery while others struggle will give the nation greater influence on the world stage. However, this also puts it on a collision course with its rivals.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n甚至有啲死唔斷氣既學者係咁吹奏中國成功控制疫情唔係因為極權主義而係跟規則做野.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 <a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/williamhaseltine/2021/01/14/why-america-should-look-to-china-to-contain-covid-19/?sh=7177c988501f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fwilliamhaseltine%2F2021%2F01%2F14%2Fwhy-america-should-look-to-china-to-contain-covid-19%2F%3Fsh%3D7177c988501f&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=a4fb6f97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/williamhaseltine/2021/01/14/why-america-should-look-to-china-to-contain-covid-19/?sh=7177c988501f</a><br />\n<br />\n而同時, 又不缺中國要封城既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20210114/china-covid-lockdown/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20210114%2Fchina-covid-lockdown%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=c8df56d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20210114/china-covid-lockdown/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有, 就係聽好多大陸人, 藍絲話中國好安全. 寧願放棄香港, 甚至外國生活都要番中國保命.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁竟然係發生咩撚野事? 有冇巴絲分享下入面既情況?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289f456116246842bff2a42e7366ee8f03ce520f","tid":2368270,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"中共行動太快，唔太睇好會全國大爆發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef0bda235de1beab6488db95d803a0bbcbccb8e","tid":2368270,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"武漢都控制到&hellip;&hellip;其他城市easy啦"},{"pid":"7fee47fc6b1f9527efaad381d774ef54d868837a","tid":2368270,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"以其他國家個感染速度<br />\n如果係大爆扮無事既，咁扮左成年而家傳到幾多人有?"},{"pid":"eeb53c9abcdb1a2f25b9299922e86ee924252d7a","tid":2368270,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fee47fc6b1f9527efaad381d774ef54d868837a","tid":2368270,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"以其他國家個感染速度<br />\n如果係大爆扮無事既，咁扮左成年而家傳到幾多人有?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"年頭統計學巴打預測，14億已經染晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0sq9Py.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0sq9Py.png&h=992bf464&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2780982ebfff16598af2be45e46f61d738b6c3e4","tid":2368270,"uid":107686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc